            {
               "text": "### Images from Archive\n\nThese images are copyright for Archive and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\">\n<div class=\"htSlide\">\n<div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 4</div>\n<img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBRES140\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBRES140', '0%')\">\n<div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Excerpt from the letter written by Christopher Columbus, where he describes islands populated with numerous people.</div>\n<div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>Who ... ?: Who truly discovered América (Abya Yala)? - This text explores the concept of discovery and questions who truly arrived first in the Americas. (<htcite0>)</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"htSlide\">\n<div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 4</div>\n<img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgLL\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgLL', '0%')\">\n<div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Lucrecia Leme, member of the Lem/Leme family.</div>\n<div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>Family: Lem/Leme - We explore the family’s history, including their involvement in the Treaty of Tordesillas and the Paulista Civil War. (<htcite1>)</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"htSlide\">\n<div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 4</div>\n<img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPD\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPD', '0%')\">\n<div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Excerpt from the inventory of Pedro Dias.</div>\n<div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>Pedro Dias: We examine the different historical versions attributed to this individual, including information from the inventory records. (<htcite3>)</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"htSlide\">\n<div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 4</div>\n<img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"Experiment\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('Experiment', '0%')\">\n<div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Optical diagram from the work of Ibn al-Haytham (Alhazen).</div>\n<div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>Scientific method: This text studies the work of Ibn Al-Haytham and describes the development of the scientific method. (<htcite2>)</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i>\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i>\n</div></p>",
